vement for search and menu element applied.\r</li></li></ul><h4 class=\"aux-changelog-item-title\"><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-version\">Version <strong>2.5.11</strong></span><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-date\">(03.05.2020)</span></h4><ul><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-new\">New</span> New responsive table element added.\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-improvement\">Improve</span> Improvements in appear animation for header builder applied.\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-improvement\">Improve</span> Improvements for Modern button element applied.\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-fix\">Fix</span> Incompatibility notice in WooCommerce setup wizard fixed.\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-fix\">Fix</span> Website social options are going to be deprecated soon.</li></ul><h4 class=\"aux-changelog-item-title\"><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-version\">Version <strong>2.5.10</strong></span><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-date\">(29.04.2020)</span></h4><ul><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-new\">New</span> New Elementor element \"Responsive Table\" added.\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-improvement\">Improve</span> Automatically turn off the sidebar in the search result page if no widget is set for the sidebar.\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-improvement\">Improve</span> Some minor improvements for Modern button applied.\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-fix\">Fix</span> Fixing an issue that results in the missing featured image for custom post types.\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-fix\">Fix</span> Remove focus outline from accordion and FAQ element.</li></ul>', 'no'),
